         <div class="sfContentBlock">
          <h1>
           All the protection you need under one roof
          </h1>
          <p>
           The National Federation of Roofing Contractors Limited (NFRC) is the UKs largest roofing trade association, representing over 70% of the roofing industry by value. With a history spanning almost 120 years, NFRC has established itself as the voice of the roofing industry, constantly adapting to change and innovation to ensure its members are at the forefront.
          </p>
          <p>
           Here you can find:
          </p>
          <ul>
           <li>
            <a href="/why-you-should-choose-an-nfrc-contractor">
             Why you should use an NFRC member
            </a>
           </li>
           <li>
            <a href="/search-members">
             Members in your local area
            </a>
           </li>
           <li>
            <a href="/join-nfrc">
             How to join NFRC
            </a>
           </li>
           <li>
            <a href="/media-centre">
             Latest news and events
            </a>
           </li>
          </ul>
          <p>
           We hope that you will find what you need within our website. If not, please
           <a href="c3f990cf-cc9f-4f4b-a189-4851736b8fa5">
            contact us
           </a>
           and we'll do our best to assist.
          </p>
          <p>
           NFRC has also been given Government approval to run a Competent Person Scheme for Roofing allowing professional roofing contractors to self-certify for Building Regulations for refurbishment work. To find out more information and visit the CompetentRoofer website please
           <a href="http://www.competentroofer.co.uk">
            click here
           </a>
           .
          </p>
